data.description: Welcome Home to 144 Loudon Road!  This well-maintained brick spilt level is conveniently located near Downtown Mercersburg and near shopping and conveniences.  Hardwood floors on multiple levels, this home features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, multiple patios and a large backyard.  A flexible floorplan offers room to roam and breakout space for everyone.  The Living Room has an awesome picture window with tons of natural light spilling in.  Kitchen features some newer stainless steel appliances . Just off the Family Room is a full bath and another patio to the backyard.  Side entry garage is currently utilized as laundry and more storage and is the partial basement.  Upstairs you'll find 3 nice-sized bedrooms with 1 full bath and 1 half bath.  NEW roof in 2021 / new sewer main line ($35k!)  / new stainless fridge & stovetop (not yet installed - still in box) / landscaping updates. Schedule your showing today!
